\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.2vob68tjqpejf.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"fixed inset-x-0 top-0 z-50 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#05070A]/70 backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex h-20 max-w-7xl items-center justify-between px-6 md:h-28 md:px-8\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"flex items-center md:self-end md:pb-4\"><img alt=\"3rd-AI\" width=\"140\" height=\"36\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent;width:clamp(140px, 14vw, 170px);height:auto\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75\"/></a><nav class=\"hidden items-center gap-12 text-sm font-medium text-slate-400 md:flex\"><a href=\"/#architecture\" class=\"transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-white\">Architecture</a><a href=\"/#platform\" class=\"transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-white\">Platform</a><a href=\"/#validation\" class=\"transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-white\">Validation</a><a href=\"/#contact\" class=\"transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-white\">Contact</a><a href=\"/about\" class=\"transition-colors duration-300 hover:text-white\">About</a></nav><a href=\"/#contact\" class=\"hidden rounded-full border border-cyan-400/60 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-cyan-300 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-cyan-300 hover:bg-cyan-400 hover:text-black md:block\">Technical Briefing</a><button class=\"flex h-10 w-10 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-1.5 rounded-lg md:hidden\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><span class=\"block h-0.5 w-6 bg-white transition-all duration-300 \"></span><span class=\"block h-0.5 w-6 bg-white transition-all duration-300 \"></span><span class=\"block h-0.5 w-6 bg-white transition-all duration-300 \"></span></button></div></header><div class=\"fixed inset-x-0 top-20 z-40 border-b border-white/5 bg-[#05070A]/95 backdrop-blur-xl transition-all duration-300 md:hidden\n          opacity-0 -translate-y-2 pointer-events-none\"><nav class=\"flex flex-col px-6 py-6 gap-1\"><a href=\"/#architecture\" class=\"rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-300 transition-colors hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\">Architecture</a><a href=\"/#platform\" class=\"rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-300 transition-colors hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\">Platform</a><a href=\"/#validation\" class=\"rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-300 transition-colors hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\">Validation</a><a href=\"/#contact\" class=\"rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-300 transition-colors hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\">Contact</a><a href=\"/about\" class=\"rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-base font-medium text-slate-300 transition-colors hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-white\">About</a><a href=\"/#contact\" class=\"mt-4 rounded-full border border-cyan-400/60 px-5 py-3 text-center text-sm font-medium text-cyan-300 transition-all hover:bg-cyan-400 hover:text-black\">Technical Briefing</a></nav></div><main class=\"bg-black\"><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden bg-black pt-32 md:pt-56 pb-8 md:pb-24\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_20%_50%,rgba(34,211,238,0.07),transparent_60%)]\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_80%_20%,rgba(59,130,246,0.05),transparent_55%)]\"></div><div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p class=\"mb-6 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-cyan-400\">About 3rd-AI</p></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h1 class=\"max-w-4xl text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-[0.94] tracking-tight text-white xl:text-7xl\">Networks grew smarter.<!-- --> <span class=\"text-cyan-400\">The systems managing them didn&#x27;t.</span></h1></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><p class=\"mt-10 max-w-2xl text-xl leading-9 text-slate-400\">3rd-AI was built to close that gap — bringing Ambient Intelligence to connected infrastructure so it can sense, understand, orchestrate, and adapt without waiting for a human to tell it to.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"relative py-12 md:py-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-16 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-24\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white\">Founding Story</h2><div class=\"mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-400\"><p>After years at the intersection of telecom operations and software, one contradiction became impossible to ignore. Operators were deploying the most sophisticated connected infrastructure ever built — Wi-Fi 7, 5G, edge compute — while the systems responsible for managing it remained largely unchanged from a previous era. The intelligence layer had been left behind.</p><p>3rd-AI was founded on the conviction that this gap can be closed. That connected infrastructure — the access points, the routers, the edge devices already deployed in homes and buildings around the world — carries enough signal to understand its own environment. And that understanding should translate directly into action, quietly and continuously, without human intervention, without cloud dependency, and without changing a single piece of hardware.</p></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-cyan-400/40 bg-[#030508] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-cyan-400/80\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-cyan-400/50\">01</span><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-white\">Infrastructure should think for itself</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Connected environments generate enough signal to understand their own state. Acting on that signal shouldn&#x27;t require a human in the loop.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-cyan-400/40 bg-[#030508] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-cyan-400/80\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-cyan-400/50\">02</span><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-white\">Privacy is non-negotiable</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">All inference runs locally on the device. Network traffic data never leaves the device — zero cloud egress, by architecture.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-cyan-400/40 bg-[#030508] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-cyan-400/80\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-cyan-400/50\">03</span><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-white\">The incumbent model is broken</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Telecom OSS/BSS vendors have locked innovation out of the management layer for decades. 3rd-AI exists to prove there&#x27;s a better way.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-cyan-400/40 bg-[#030508] p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-cyan-400/80\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><span class=\"mt-0.5 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-cyan-400/50\">04</span><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-white\">Energy efficiency is a first-class outcome</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-400\">Autonomous optimization isn&#x27;t just operationally better — it measurably reduces energy consumption and carbon emissions at fleet scale.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative py-12 md:py-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-cyan-400/20 bg-cyan-400/5 p-12 text-center\"><p class=\"mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-cyan-400/70\">Our Mission</p><p class=\"mx-auto max-w-3xl text-2xl font-semibold leading-snug text-white lg:text-3xl\">To bring Ambient Intelligence to connected environments — enabling infrastructure to sense, understand, orchestrate, and adapt<!-- --> <span class=\"text-cyan-400\">autonomously.</span></p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-12 md:py-24\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8 text-center\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-semibold text-white\">Ready to see it in action?</h2><p class=\"mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-lg text-slate-400\">Explore the platform or get in touch with our team for a technical briefing.</p><div class=\"mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4\"><a href=\"/#platform\" class=\"rounded-full bg-cyan-400 px-7 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-black transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105\">Explore the Platform</a><a href=\"/#contact\" class=\"rounded-full border border-white/15 px-7 py-3.5 text-base text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:border-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-400\">Request a Technical Briefing</a></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"border-t border-white/5 bg-[#05070A] py-12\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl px-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-8 md:flex-row md:items-start md:justify-between\"><div><a href=\"/\" class=\"inline-flex items-center self-end\"><img alt=\"3rd-AI\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"30\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" style=\"color:transparent;width:120px;height:auto\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Flogo.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></a><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-xs text-sm leading-6 text-slate-500\">Ambient Intelligence for connected environments.</p></div><nav class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-x-10 gap-y-3 text-sm text-slate-500\"><a href=\"/#architecture\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">Architecture</a><a href=\"/#platform\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">Platform</a><a href=\"/#validation\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">Validation</a><a href=\"/#contact\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">Contact</a><a href=\"/about\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">About</a><a href=\"/privacy\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">Privacy Policy</a><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/3rd-ai.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"transition-colors hover:text-slate-300\">LinkedIn</a></nav></div><div class=\"my-8 h-px bg-white/5\"></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 text-xs text-slate-600\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> 3rd-AI Limited. All rights reserved.</p><p class=\"mt-2 max-w-2xl leading-5 md:mt-0\">Projected figures are based on modelled deployment scenarios and do not represent guaranteed outcomes. Statements regarding future capabilities are forward-looking and subject to change.</p><p class=\"leading-5\">3rd-AI Limited · Registered in England &amp; Wales · Company No. 16341261</p></div></div></footer><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/1guoti84v2fh3.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1d4h-sglyo8ft.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/3jupxlga7r_do.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1d4h-sglyo8ft.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/3jupxlga7r_do.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[7988,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1d4h-sglyo8ft.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/3jupxlga7r_do.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/3vxl_ykt3m0uw.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1zdpv00h2h6hi.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[4376,[\\\"/_next/stat